## 📊 TELEMETRY REQUIREMENTS

Every operation must log:
```json
{
  "operation": "code_generation",
  "agent": "Δ|Ω|👁|Κ",
  "token_cost": 0.15,
  "latency_ms": 2500,
  "entropy_delta": -0.3,
  "floors_checked": ["F2", "F4", "F7"],
  "verdict": "SEAL|SABAR|VOID"
}
```

